{"word":"ἄποψις","slug":"ἄποψις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄποψις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἀπόψομαι</el>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> of <a href='S:ἀφοράω'><el>ἀφοράω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>an outlook, view, prospect</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a lofty spot</i> or <i>tower which commands a view</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}